info.description:
******************************************
# IBM Watson OpenScale Utilities
******************************************

`ibm-wos-utils` is a utility library used to create multiple artifacts required by IBM Watson OpenScale.

## Important Notice:

* If you are using **IBM Watson OpenScale on Cloud Pak for Data 3.0.x or 3.5.x**, please install [ibm-wos-utils v2.1.1](https://pypi.org/project/ibm-wos-utils/2.1.1/). Drift Archive generation requires [scikit-learn v0.20.2](https://pypi.org/project/scikit-learn/0.20.2/) for these releases.

* If you are using **IBM Watson OpenScale on Cloud Pak for Data 3.5.10 or later**, please install [ibm-wos-utils v2.1.5](https://pypi.org/project/ibm-wos-utils/2.1.5/). Drift Archive generation requires [scikit-learn v0.24.2](https://pypi.org/project/scikit-learn/0.24.2/) for these releases.

* If you are using **IBM Watson OpenScale on Cloud Pak for Data 4.0.0, 4.0.1, 4.0.2, 4.0.3, 4.0.4, 4.0.5, 4.0.6, 4.0.7**, please install the [ibm-wos-utils v4.0.34](https://pypi.org/project/ibm-wos-utils/4.0.34/). Drift Archive generation requires [scikit-learn v0.24.2](https://pypi.org/project/scikit-learn/0.24.2/) for these releases.

* If you are using **IBM Watson OpenScale on Cloud Pak for Data 4.0.8 or 4.0.9**, please install the [ibm-wos-utils version 4.1.x](https://pypi.org/project/ibm-wos-utils/). Drift Archive generation requires [scikit-learn v1.0.2](https://pypi.org/project/scikit-learn/1.0.2/) for these releases.

* If you are using **IBM Watson OpenScale on Cloud Pak for Data 4.5.0 or later** or **IBM Watson OpenScale on Cloud**, please install the [latest ibm-wos-utils version 4.5.x](https://pypi.org/project/ibm-wos-utils/). Drift Archive generation requires [scikit-learn v1.0.2](https://pypi.org/project/scikit-learn/1.0.2/) for Cloud.
